\c 45
\s Ilizwi likaJeremiya kuBharukhi
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi uJeremiya umprofethi alikhuluma kuBharukhi indodana kaNeriya,\x + 32.12.\x* ekubhaleni kwakhe lamazwi egwalweni evela emlonyeni kaJeremiya,\x + 36.4.\x* ngomnyaka wesine kaJehoyakhimi, indodana kaJosiya, inkosi yakoJuda,\x + 36.1.\x* lisithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kuwe Bharukhi:
\v 3 Uthi wena: Hawu maye mina, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yengezelela usizi ebuhlungwini bami,\x + 36.26.\x* sengikhathele yikububula kwami,\x + Lilo 5.5.\x* njalo kangitholi\x + Lilo 1.3.\x* ukuphumula.\x + 51.59.\x*
\v 4 Uzakutsho njalo kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, lokho engikwakhileyo ngiyakudiliza,\x + 1.10. Isa. 5.5.\x* lalokho engikuhlanyeleyo ngiyakusiphuna; yebo, ilizwe leli lonke.
\v 5 Wena-ke uzazidingela izinto ezinkulu yini?\x + 51.59. Hlab. 131.2\x* Ungazidingi; ngoba khangela, ngiletha okubi phezu kwayo yonke inyama,\x + 25.26,31.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*; kodwa ngizakunika impilo yakho ibe yimpango kuzo zonke indawo lapho oya khona.\x + 21.9.\x*